  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IRF 5 - Providing life-saving and humanitarian relief to communities affected by drought in Somalia/ Pre-famine response</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is intended to provide safety nets through cash support for drought affected vulnerable rural and IDP households in Mudug, Galgadud and Bari regions of Somalia, WASH support to drought affected households from Galgaduud region (Adado district ) and essential lifesaving healthcare and nutrition services to IDPs and host community populations of Gaalkacyo, Dhusamareb and Guriel districts of Somalia.</narrative>
  </description>
